cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CC, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a mixed physical-virtual technology to stimulate social interactions among older adults in nursing homes. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper addresses social issues related to institutionalized care and proposes a technological solution. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper investigates social interactions among older adults and how technology can facilitate them. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.GR (Graphics) are less likely categories as they are not directly related to the topic of the paper.
